术水平紧追业内一线，如此的团队在长期来看才更易于沉淀技术积累，而技术积累对于以技术为核心的互联网公司亦是命脉之一。","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1049180,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/02/5c/13332f45.jpg","nickname":"黄勇","note":"","ucode":"8488CFA31F9A09","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":461209,"discussion_content":"我们是工程师，不是一般的程序员。我认为，工程师需要有工程性思维，更高级的工程师还需要有商业性思维，知道自己写的代码如何去变现。所以，告诉工程师代码怎样实现商业价值，这件事儿就很有意义。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1564826844,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":120782,"user_name":"w*waiting","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1121924,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8896200CF6A8AF","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/1e/84/03053efe.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1564994947,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":44358,"content":"不错哦👍","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"黄勇","uid":1049180,"ctime":1565006964,"ip_address":"","comment_id":120782,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100030701,"comment_content":"外包公司：\n最后O的制定，如果跟线上运营情况进行相关的话，感觉找不到抓手。\n我有一个想法，是不是可以跟开发流程相关；\nO-优化开发流程：项目开发完成后，两周内完成项目验收，并回款\nKR1-一周内让客户满意，完成验收；\nKR2-两周内想办法要回款。","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1049180,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/02/5c/13332f45.jpg","nickname":"黄勇","note":"","ucode":"8488CFA31F9A09","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":461477,"discussion_content":"不错哦👍","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1565006964,